==English==
===Noun===
'''tosser'''

# (''Mainly British slang'') Someone who [[masturbates]]
# (''Mainly British slang'') Someone the [[speaker]] doesn't like
#: ''that bloke who ripped me off was a right tosser''
#To Toss is to Masturbate; The term however, is some times confused, or even interchangeable  with, [[Tosspot]], meaning a drunkard or heavy drinker. As the terms are intentionally abusive, either is acceptable as a formal insult, although it should be noted that, similarities apart, the two words do have different meanings.